{"code":200,"status":"OK","data":{"number":202,"ayahs":[{"number":4531,"audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/4531.mp3","audioSecondary":["https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/64/ar.alafasy/4531.mp3"],"text":"۞ وَٱذْكُرْ أَخَا عَادٍ إِذْ أَنذَرَ قَوْمَهُۥ بِٱلْأَحْقَافِ وَقَدْ خَلَتِ ٱلنُّذُرُ مِنۢ بَيْنِ يَدَيْهِ وَمِنْ خَلْفِهِۦٓ أَلَّا تَعْبُدُوٓا۟ إِلَّا ٱللَّهَ إِنِّىٓ أَخَافُ عَلَيْكُمْ عَذَابَ يَوْمٍ عَظِيمٍۢ","numberInSurah":21,"juz":26,"manzil":6,"page":505,"ruku":440,"hizbQuarter":202,"sajda":false,"surah":{"number":46,"name":"سُورَةُ الأَحۡقَافِ","englishName":"Al-Ahqaf","englishNameTranslation":"The Dunes","revelationType":"Meccan"}},{"number":4532,"audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/4532.mp3","audioSecondary":["https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/64/ar.alafasy/4532.mp3"],"text":"قَالُوٓا۟ أَجِئْتَنَا لِتَأْفِكَنَا عَنْ ءَالِهَتِنَا فَأْتِنَا بِمَا تَعِدُنَآ إِن كُنتَ مِنَ ٱلصَّٰدِقِينَ","numberInSurah":22,"juz":26,"manzil":6,"page":505,"ruku":440,"hizbQuarter":202,"sajda":false,"surah":{"number":46,"name":"سُورَةُ الأَحۡقَافِ","englishName":"Al-Ahqaf","englishNameTranslation":"The Dunes","revelationType":"Meccan"}},{"number":4533,"audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/4533.mp3","audioSecondary":["https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/64/ar.alafasy/4533.mp3"],"text":"قَالَ إِنَّمَا ٱلْعِلْمُ عِندَ ٱللَّهِ وَأُبَلِّغُكُم مَّآ أُرْسِلْتُ بِهِۦ وَلَٰكِنِّىٓ أَرَىٰكُمْ قَوْمًۭا تَجْهَلُونَ","numberInSurah":23,"juz":26,"manzil":6,"page":505,"ruku":440,"hizbQuarter":202,"sajda":false,"surah":{"number":46,"name":"سُورَةُ الأَحۡقَافِ","englishName":"Al-Ahqaf","englishNameTranslation":"The Dunes","revelationType":"Meccan"}},{"number":4534,"audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/4534.mp3","audioSecondary":["https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/64/ar.alafasy/4534.mp3"],"text":"فَلَمَّا رَأَوْهُ عَارِضًۭا مُّسْتَقْبِلَ أَوْدِيَتِهِمْ قَالُوا۟ هَٰذَا عَارِضٌۭ مُّمْطِرُنَا ۚ بَلْ هُوَ مَا ٱسْتَعْجَلْتُم بِهِۦ ۖ رِيحٌۭ فِيهَا عَذَابٌ أَلِيمٌۭ","numberInSurah":24,"juz":26,"manzil":6,"page":505,"ruku":440,"hizbQuarter":202,"sajda":false,"surah":{"number":46,"name":"سُورَةُ الأَحۡقَافِ","englishName":"Al-Ahqaf","englishNameTranslation":"The Dunes","revelationType":"Meccan"}},{"number":4535,"audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/4535.mp3","audioSecondary":["https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/64/ar.alafasy/4535.mp3"],"text":"تُدَمِّرُ كُلَّ شَىْءٍۭ بِأَمْرِ رَبِّهَا فَأَصْبَحُوا۟ لَا يُرَىٰٓ إِلَّا مَسَٰكِنُهُمْ ۚ كَذَٰلِكَ نَجْزِى ٱلْقَوْمَ ٱلْمُجْرِمِينَ","numberInSurah":25,"juz":26,"manzil":6,"page":505,"ruku":440,"hizbQuarter":202,"sajda":false,"surah":{"number":46,"name":"سُورَةُ الأَحۡقَافِ","englishName":"Al-Ahqaf","englishNameTranslation":"The Dunes","revelationType":"Meccan"}},{"number":4536,"audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/4536.mp3","audioSecondary":["https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/64/ar.alafasy/4536.mp3"],"text":"وَلَقَدْ مَكَّنَّٰهُمْ فِيمَآ إِن مَّكَّنَّٰكُمْ فِيهِ وَجَعَلْنَا لَهُمْ سَمْعًۭا وَأَبْصَٰرًۭا وَأَفْـِٔدَةًۭ فَمَآ أَغْنَىٰ عَنْهُمْ سَمْعُهُمْ وَلَآ أَبْصَٰرُهُمْ وَلَآ أَفْـِٔدَتُهُم مِّن شَىْءٍ إِذْ كَانُوا۟ يَجْحَدُونَ بِـَٔايَٰتِ ٱللَّهِ وَحَاقَ بِهِم مَّا كَانُوا۟ بِهِۦ يَسْتَهْزِءُونَ","numberInSurah":26,"juz":26,"manzil":6,"page":505,"ruku":440,"hizbQuarter":202,"sajda":false,"surah":{"number":46,"name":"سُورَةُ الأَحۡقَافِ","englishName":"Al-Ahqaf","englishNameTranslation":"The Dunes","revelationType":"Meccan"}},{"number":4537,"audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/4537.mp3","audioSecondary":["https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/64/ar.alafasy/4537.mp3"],"text":"وَلَقَدْ أَهْلَكْنَا مَا حَوْلَكُم مِّنَ ٱلْقُرَىٰ وَصَرَّفْنَا ٱلْءَايَٰتِ لَعَلَّهُمْ يَرْجِعُونَ","numberInSurah":27,"juz":26,"manzil":6,"page":505,"ruku":441,"hizbQuarter":202,"sajda":false,"surah":{"number":46,"name":"سُورَةُ الأَحۡقَافِ","englishName":"Al-Ahqaf","englishNameTranslation":"The Dunes","revelationType":"Meccan"}},{"number":4538,"audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/4538.mp3","audioSecondary":["https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/64/ar.alafasy/4538.mp3"],"text":"فَلَوْلَا نَصَرَهُمُ ٱلَّذِينَ ٱتَّخَذُوا۟ مِن دُونِ ٱللَّهِ قُرْبَانًا ءَالِهَةًۢ ۖ بَلْ ضَلُّوا۟ عَنْهُمْ ۚ وَذَٰلِكَ إِفْكُهُمْ وَمَا كَانُوا۟ يَفْتَرُونَ","numberInSurah":28,"juz":26,"manzil":6,"page":505,"ruku":441,"hizbQuarter":202,"sajda":false,"surah":{"number":46,"name":"سُورَةُ الأَحۡقَافِ","englishName":"Al-Ahqaf","englishNameTranslation":"The Dunes","revelationType":"Meccan"}},{"number":4539,"audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/4539.mp3","audioSecondary":["https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/64/ar.alafasy/4539.mp3"],"text":"وَإِذْ صَرَفْنَآ إِلَيْكَ نَفَرًۭا مِّنَ ٱلْجِنِّ يَسْتَمِعُونَ ٱلْقُرْءَانَ فَلَمَّا حَضَرُوهُ قَالُوٓا۟ أَنصِتُوا۟ ۖ فَلَمَّا قُضِىَ وَلَّوْا۟ إِلَىٰ قَوْمِهِم مُّنذِرِينَ","numberInSurah":29,"juz":26,"manzil":6,"page":506,"ruku":441,"hizbQuarter":202,"sajda":false,"surah":{"number":46,"name":"سُورَةُ الأَحۡقَافِ","englishName":"Al-Ahqaf","englishNameTranslation":"The Dunes","revelationType":"Meccan"}},{"number":4540,"audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/4540.mp3","audioSecondary":["https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/64/ar.alafasy/4540.mp3"],"text":"قَالُوا۟ يَٰقَوْمَنَآ إِنَّا سَمِعْنَا كِتَٰبًا أُنزِلَ مِنۢ بَعْدِ مُوسَىٰ مُصَدِّقًۭا لِّمَا بَيْنَ يَدَيْهِ يَهْدِىٓ إِلَى ٱلْحَقِّ وَإِلَىٰ طَرِيقٍۢ مُّسْتَقِيمٍۢ","numberInSurah":30,"juz":26,"manzil":6,"page":506,"ruku":441,"hizbQuarter":202,"sajda":false,"surah":{"number":46,"name":"سُورَةُ الأَحۡقَافِ","englishName":"Al-Ahqaf","englishNameTranslation":"The Dunes","revelationType":"Meccan"}},{"number":4541,"audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/4541.mp3","audioSecondary":["https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/64/ar.alafasy/4541.mp3"],"text":"يَٰقَوْمَنَآ أَجِيبُوا۟ دَاعِىَ ٱللَّهِ وَءَامِنُوا۟ بِهِۦ يَغْفِرْ لَكُم مِّن ذُنُوبِكُمْ وَيُجِرْكُم مِّنْ عَذَابٍ أَلِيمٍۢ","numberInSurah":31,"juz":26,"manzil":6,"page":506,"ruku":441,"hizbQuarter":202,"sajda":false,"surah":{"number":46,"name":"سُورَةُ الأَحۡقَافِ","englishName":"Al-Ahqaf","englishNameTranslation":"The Dunes","revelationType":"Meccan"}},{"number":4542,"audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/4542.mp3","audioSecondary":["https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/64/ar.alafasy/4542.mp3"],"text":"وَمَن لَّا يُجِبْ دَاعِىَ ٱللَّهِ فَلَيْسَ بِمُعْجِزٍۢ فِى ٱلْأَرْضِ وَلَيْسَ لَهُۥ مِن دُونِهِۦٓ أَوْلِيَآءُ ۚ أُو۟لَٰٓئِكَ فِى ضَلَٰلٍۢ مُّبِينٍ","numberInSurah":32,"juz":26,"manzil":6,"page":506,"ruku":441,"hizbQuarter":202,"sajda":false,"surah":{"number":46,"name":"سُورَةُ الأَحۡقَافِ","englishName":"Al-Ahqaf","englishNameTranslation":"The Dunes","revelationType":"Meccan"}},{"number":4543,"audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/4543.mp3","audioSecondary":["https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/64/ar.alafasy/4543.mp3"],"text":"أَوَلَمْ يَرَوْا۟ أَنَّ ٱللَّهَ ٱلَّذِى خَلَقَ ٱلسَّمَٰوَٰتِ وَٱلْأَرْضَ وَلَمْ يَعْىَ بِخَلْقِهِنَّ بِقَٰدِرٍ عَلَىٰٓ أَن يُحْۦِىَ ٱلْمَوْتَىٰ ۚ بَلَىٰٓ إِنَّهُۥ عَلَىٰ كُلِّ شَىْءٍۢ قَدِيرٌۭ","numberInSurah":33,"juz":26,"manzil":6,"page":506,"ruku":441,"hizbQuarter":202,"sajda":false,"surah":{"number":46,"name":"سُورَةُ الأَحۡقَافِ","englishName":"Al-Ahqaf","englishNameTranslation":"The Dunes","revelationType":"Meccan"}},{"number":4544,"audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/4544.mp3","audioSecondary":["https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/64/ar.alafasy/4544.mp3"],"text":"وَيَوْمَ يُعْرَضُ ٱلَّذِينَ كَفَرُوا۟ عَلَى ٱلنَّارِ أَلَيْسَ هَٰذَا بِٱلْحَقِّ ۖ قَالُوا۟ بَلَىٰ وَرَبِّنَا ۚ قَالَ فَذُوقُوا۟ ٱلْعَذَابَ بِمَا كُنتُمْ تَكْفُرُونَ","numberInSurah":34,"juz":26,"manzil":6,"page":506,"ruku":441,"hizbQuarter":202,"sajda":false,"surah":{"number":46,"name":"سُورَةُ الأَحۡقَافِ","englishName":"Al-Ahqaf","englishNameTranslation":"The Dunes","revelationType":"Meccan"}},{"number":4545,"audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/4545.mp3","audioSecondary":["https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/64/ar.alafasy/4545.mp3"],"text":"فَٱصْبِرْ كَمَا صَبَرَ أُو۟لُوا۟ ٱلْعَزْمِ مِنَ ٱلرُّسُلِ وَلَا تَسْتَعْجِل لَّهُمْ ۚ كَأَنَّهُمْ يَوْمَ يَرَوْنَ مَا يُوعَدُونَ لَمْ يَلْبَثُوٓا۟ إِلَّا سَاعَةًۭ مِّن نَّهَارٍۭ ۚ بَلَٰغٌۭ ۚ فَهَلْ يُهْلَكُ إِلَّا ٱلْقَوْمُ ٱلْفَٰسِقُونَ","numberInSurah":35,"juz":26,"manzil":6,"page":506,"ruku":441,"hizbQuarter":202,"sajda":false,"surah":{"number":46,"name":"سُورَةُ الأَحۡقَافِ","englishName":"Al-Ahqaf","englishNameTranslation":"The Dunes","revelationType":"Meccan"}},{"number":4546,"audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/4546.mp3","audioSecondary":["https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/64/ar.alafasy/4546.mp3"],"text":"بِسْمِ ٱللَّهِ ٱلرَّحْمَٰنِ ٱلرَّحِيمِ ٱلَّذِينَ كَفَرُوا۟ وَصَدُّوا۟ عَن سَبِيلِ ٱللَّهِ أَضَلَّ أَعْمَٰلَهُمْ","numberInSurah":1,"juz":26,"manzil":6,"page":507,"ruku":442,"hizbQuarter":202,"sajda":false,"surah":{"number":47,"name":"سُورَةُ مُحَمَّدٍ","englishName":"Muhammad","englishNameTranslation":"Muhammad","revelationType":"Medinan"}},{"number":4547,"audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/4547.mp3","audioSecondary":["https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/64/ar.alafasy/4547.mp3"],"text":"وَٱلَّذِينَ ءَامَنُوا۟ وَعَمِلُوا۟ ٱلصَّٰلِحَٰتِ وَءَامَنُوا۟ بِمَا نُزِّلَ عَلَىٰ مُحَمَّدٍۢ وَهُوَ ٱلْحَقُّ مِن رَّبِّهِمْ ۙ كَفَّرَ عَنْهُمْ سَيِّـَٔاتِهِمْ وَأَصْلَحَ بَالَهُمْ","numberInSurah":2,"juz":26,"manzil":6,"page":507,"ruku":442,"hizbQuarter":202,"sajda":false,"surah":{"number":47,"name":"سُورَةُ مُحَمَّدٍ","englishName":"Muhammad","englishNameTranslation":"Muhammad","revelationType":"Medinan"}},{"number":4548,"audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/4548.mp3"